<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

.nv-faq-wrap {
  width: 100%;
  background: #fff;
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
  padding: 80px 40px 120px;
}

.nv-faq-inner {
  max-width: 760px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.nv-faq-page-title {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.36em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #111;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 72px;
}

.nv-faq-category {
  margin-bottom: 0;
  border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
}

.nv-faq-category:last-child {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
}

.nv-faq-cat-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 22px 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  user-select: none;
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}

.nv-faq-category.is-open .nv-faq-cat-header {
  border-bottom-color: #e5e5e5;
}

.nv-faq-cat-title {
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #111;
}

.nv-faq-cat-icon {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #111;
  line-height: 1;
  transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.77,0,0.175,1);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.nv-faq-category.is-open .nv-faq-cat-icon {
  transform: rotate(45deg);
}

.nv-faq-cat-body {
  display: none;
  padding-bottom: 8px;
}

.nv-faq-category.is-open .nv-faq-cat-body {
  display: block;
}

.nv-faq-item {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
}

.nv-faq-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.nv-faq-q {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 18px 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  user-select: none;
  gap: 20px;
}

.nv-faq-q-text {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #111;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.nv-faq-q-icon {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #888;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  line-height: 1;
  transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.77,0,0.175,1);
}

.nv-faq-item.is-open .nv-faq-q-icon {
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  color: #111;
}

.nv-faq-a {
  display: none;
  padding: 0 0 20px;
}

.nv-faq-item.is-open .nv-faq-a {
  display: block;
}

.nv-faq-a p {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: #555;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.nv-faq-contact-strip {
  margin-top: 72px;
  padding: 40px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  text-align: center;
}

.nv-faq-contact-text {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #777;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.nv-faq-contact-link {
  display: inline-block;
  background: #111;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 16px 40px;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  border: 1px solid #111;
  font-family: 'Inter', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
  transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
}

.nv-faq-contact-link:hover {
  background: #fff;
  color: #111;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .nv-faq-wrap { padding: 56px 20px 80px; }
  .nv-faq-page-title { margin-bottom: 48px; }
}
</style>

<div class="nv-faq-wrap">
  <div class="nv-faq-inner">

    <p class="nv-faq-page-title">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</p>

    <!-- 1. ORDERS & AVAILABILITY -->
    <div class="nv-faq-category" id="nv-cat-1">
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-header" data-cat="nv-cat-1">
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-title">01 — ORDERS & AVAILABILITY</span>
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-body">
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHY ARE PRODUCTS LIMITED?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>EACH NALVIK PIECE IS PRODUCED IN SMALL BATCHES. QUANTITIES ARE INTENTIONALLY RESTRICTED.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WILL SOLD-OUT ITEMS RETURN?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>NO. ONCE A PIECE IS SOLD OUT, IT IS NOT REPRODUCED.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">CAN I MODIFY OR CANCEL MY ORDER?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>ORDERS MAY BE MODIFIED OR CANCELLED AFTER PLACEMENT. PLEASE CONTACT US AT THE EARLIEST. OUR STAFF WOULD BE HAPPY TO ASSIST.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">HOW DO I KNOW ABOUT NEW RELEASES?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>PLEASE SUBSCRIBE OR FOLLOW OUR UPDATES TO STAY INFORMED ABOUT UPCOMING RELEASES.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. EARLY ACCESS -->
    <div class="nv-faq-category" id="nv-cat-2">
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-header" data-cat="nv-cat-2">
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-title">02 — EARLY ACCESS</span>
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-body">
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHAT IS EARLY ACCESS?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>EARLY ACCESS IS A RESTRICTED RELEASE WINDOW OFFERED TO A LIMITED GROUP PRIOR TO PUBLIC AVAILABILITY.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHO RECEIVES EARLY ACCESS?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>ACCESS IS EXTENDED SELECTIVELY. IT IS NOT AUTOMATICALLY GRANTED.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">HOW CAN I BE CONSIDERED FOR EARLY ACCESS?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>YOU MAY KINDLY SUBMIT YOUR INTEREST BY REGISTERING YOUR EMAIL OR CONTACTING US DIRECTLY. OUR STAFF WOULD BE HAPPY TO ASSIST.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHY IS ACCESS LIMITED?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>EACH RELEASE IS PRODUCED IN SMALL QUANTITIES. LIMITING ACCESS ENSURES CONTROLLED DISTRIBUTION.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">HOW WILL I KNOW IF I'VE BEEN SELECTED?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>SELECTED INDIVIDUALS WILL BE NOTIFIED DIRECTLY VIA EMAIL.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. SHIPPING & DELIVERY -->
    <div class="nv-faq-category" id="nv-cat-3">
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-header" data-cat="nv-cat-3">
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-title">03 — SHIPPING & DELIVERY</span>
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-body">
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHERE DO YOU SHIP?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>NALVIK SHIPS WORLDWIDE. DELIVERY TIMELINES MAY VARY DEPENDING ON LOCATION AND COURIER CONDITIONS.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHAT IS THE DELIVERY TIMELINE?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>READY-TO-SHIP ORDERS ARE DELIVERED WITHIN 3–7 BUSINESS DAYS.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">HOW CAN I TRACK MY ORDER?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>A TRACKING LINK IS SHARED UPON DISPATCH. YOU WILL ALSO RECEIVE ORDER UPDATES VIA EMAIL.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHAT IF I ENTER AN INCORRECT SHIPPING ADDRESS?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>PLEASE CONTACT US IMMEDIATELY. WE WILL ASSIST IF THE ORDER HAS NOT YET BEEN DISPATCHED.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHAT IF MY ORDER IS DELAYED?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>DELAYS MAY OCCUR DUE TO COURIER OR EXTERNAL FACTORS. PLEASE ALLOW ADDITIONAL TIME WHERE REQUIRED.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. RETURNS & EXCHANGES -->
    <div class="nv-faq-category" id="nv-cat-4">
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-header" data-cat="nv-cat-4">
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-title">04 — RETURNS & EXCHANGES</span>
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-body">
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">DO YOU ACCEPT RETURNS?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>RETURNS ARE ACCEPTED ONLY FOR ITEMS THAT ARRIVE DAMAGED OR DEFECTIVE.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">DO YOU OFFER EXCHANGES?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>NO. EXCHANGES ARE NOT AVAILABLE.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHAT IF I RECEIVE A DAMAGED ITEM?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>PLEASE CONTACT US WITHIN 4 DAYS OF DELIVERY WITH SUPPORTING IMAGES. OUR STAFF WOULD BE HAPPY TO ASSIST.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 5. PAYMENTS & PRICING -->
    <div class="nv-faq-category" id="nv-cat-5">
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-header" data-cat="nv-cat-5">
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-title">05 — PAYMENTS & PRICING</span>
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-body">
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHAT PAYMENT METHODS ARE ACCEPTED?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>ALL MAJOR CARDS AND SECURE PAYMENT GATEWAYS ARE SUPPORTED.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">DO YOU OFFER DISCOUNTS?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>NO. NALVIK DOES NOT OPERATE ON A DISCOUNT MODEL.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">ARE PRICES INCLUSIVE OF TAXES?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>YES. PRICES ARE INCLUSIVE UNLESS STATED OTHERWISE. SHIPPING IS COMPLIMENTARY.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 6. SUPPORT -->
    <div class="nv-faq-category" id="nv-cat-6">
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-header" data-cat="nv-cat-6">
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-title">06 — SUPPORT</span>
        <span class="nv-faq-cat-icon">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nv-faq-cat-body">
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">HOW CAN I CONTACT NALVIK?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>PLEASE REACH US VIA <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:#111;text-decoration:underline;">THE CONTACT PAGE</a> OR DIRECTLY AT <a href="mailto:care@nalvik.com" style="color:#111;text-decoration:underline;">CARE@NALVIK.COM</a>. OUR STAFF WOULD BE HAPPY TO ASSIST.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="nv-faq-item">
          <div class="nv-faq-q"><span class="nv-faq-q-text">WHAT IS THE RESPONSE TIME?</span><span class="nv-faq-q-icon">+</span></div>
          <div class="nv-faq-a"><p>RESPONSES ARE TYPICALLY PROVIDED WITHIN 24–48 HOURS.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nv-faq-contact-strip">
      <p class="nv-faq-contact-text">STILL HAVE A QUESTION? WE'RE HERE TO HELP.</p>
      <a href="mailto:care@nalvik.com" class="nv-faq-contact-link">CONTACT US</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<script>
(function(){
  document.querySelectorAll('.nv-faq-cat-header').forEach(function(header){
    header.addEventListener('click', function(){
      var cat = document.getElementById(header.getAttribute('data-cat'));
      if(!cat) return;
      var isOpen = cat.classList.contains('is-open');
      document.querySelectorAll('.nv-faq-category').forEach(function(c){ c.classList.remove('is-open'); });
      if(!isOpen) cat.classList.add('is-open');
    });
  });

  document.querySelectorAll('.nv-faq-q').forEach(function(q){
    q.addEventListener('click', function(){
      var item = q.closest('.nv-faq-item');
      if(!item) return;
      var isOpen = item.classList.contains('is-open');
      item.closest('.nv-faq-cat-body').querySelectorAll('.nv-faq-item').forEach(function(i){ i.classList.remove('is-open'); });
      if(!isOpen) item.classList.add('is-open');
    });
  });
})();
</script>

